page.title: 11Industrial Estate
page.content:
Over the last few years, an Industrial Estate has been developed at{Holton {Heath.} The site is important because it is close to{Poole and Wareham. } There is also a railway station and good roads, which are important for transporting the goods made on the Industrial Estate, and for the people employed there.
The Estate has a wide range of industries, which{employ many people.} Not only local people are employed, but people from Bournemouth and Poole. The railway station is important for some of the people who travel to the Estate, in the early morning and early evening. However, trains do not normally stop here during the day, or at weekends.
